    .mainbody
      div
        // Heading
        .mb-4.mt-4.mx-sm.grid.grids.mxs.gaps.gaprows
          h1.col-span-full(class='md:col-span-4 mb-[15px] lg:text-bh-2xl lg:leading-[45px] xl:text-bh-3xl')
            | Huvudrubrik
          p.col-span-full.mb-10.text-bh-md.mt-2(class='md:col-start-5 md:col-span-8 lg:col-span-4 @*border-b border-bh-gray*@ @*lg:border-r lg:border-bh-gray*@ @*lg:border-b-0*@ leading-[normal]')
            | The Skanska Brand Device is a dynamic extension of the Skanska Logotype. It is a symbol that confidently adapts to various contexts and formats and adds a humble, yet confident presence as a brand sender. With it&acute;s clear and bold shapes, it tells a story of building, stability, foundation, micro, and macro perspectives and the importance of attention to detail. Our Brand Device is a set of fixed shapes, not to be altered, but adaptable in size to fit different formats, both for still and motion.
